{"type":"text","timestamp":1779200639765,"sessionID":"ses_1bf81dad4ffe1rXjRF8ncL7rCd","part":{"id":"prt_e409f1e04001UbmUHoS02RtHBt","messageID":"msg_e409f0fe2001xluvaJeKtYaOQB","sessionID":"ses_1bf81dad4ffe1rXjRF8ncL7rCd","type":"text","text":"## Integration Complete\n\n**72% coverage** — 16 of 22 pages wired to backend APIs with TanStack Query.\n\n### What was done\n\n**Infrastructure:**\n- `httpService.ts` — switched from localStorage to httpOnly cookies (`withCredentials:true`), added `_isRetry` flag to prevent infinite refresh loops (RULE-I1)\n- `providers.tsx` — wrapped app in `QueryClientProvider`\n- **6 type files** in `types/api/` — typed DTOs for auth, properties, favorites, inquiries, admin, amenities, profile\n\n**7 API service files** + **7 TanStack Query hook files** covering all 34 backend endpoints from `PROJECT_API.md`\n\n**16 wired pages** with loading/error/empty states:\n- All admin pages (dashboard, properties, property-form, inquiries, users)\n- All renter pages (search, detail, favorites)\n- All auth pages (login, register, signup, forgot-password, reset-password, admin-login)\n- Profile + Landing (featured properties)\n\n**1 skipped page:** `renter/inquiries.tsx` — needs `GET /inquiries/my` (renter-scoped inquiries list). Documented in `MISSING_ENDPOINTS.yaml` for self-healing in the next backend generation.\n\n**TypeScript:** `tsc --noEmit` passes cleanly (0 errors).","time":{"start":1779200630276,"end":1779200639762}}}
